### Registro de usuário
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "usuario teste",
    "senha": "testpassword",
    "email": "email@example.com",
    "login": "usuario_teste"
}

### Login com usuário
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "login": "usuario_teste",
    "senha": "testpassword"
}

### Login com email
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "login": "email@example.com",
    "senha": "testpassword"
}

